{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2524490, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "从概率上，如果你九个题有把握，一个题不知道，那么从数学期望上，博一下的收益是0.", "timestamp": 1631806562, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524494, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以如果九个题有把握，一个题有超过50%的正确率，从期望上收益大于0. 但问题在于 心理上100%把握不等于100%的正确率。", "timestamp": 1631806622, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524506, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "40分或2分，不博是20或18", "timestamp": 1631806666, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524521, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": 2524506, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 噢你是对的 我傻了", "timestamp": 1631806723, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524525, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": 2524490, "tag": null, "text": "那确实博的话期望是正的", "timestamp": 1631806742, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524528, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": 2524506, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: bob正解 我糊涂了", "timestamp": 1631806757, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2524870, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "全都空着是不是属于全做错了🐶🐶🐶", "timestamp": 1631808381, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2525229, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "想答错我瞎写不好吗", "timestamp": 1631809670, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2528306, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": 2525229, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 好吧，要求10个题必须作答，必须填对or错，不能不填。", "timestamp": 1631852680, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2528811, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": 2525229, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 判断题要求全错，想啥呢", "timestamp": 1631856476, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2531105, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 482157, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "Re : 事实上，不管是20分还是40分都能得到4.0，但是如果2分就完了。但是得40分爽啊！为荣誉而战！", "timestamp": 1631878281, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 1, "pid": 482157, "reply": 11, "tag": null, "text": "奇怪的出题方式1\n10个判断题，每题2分，全对拿20分。\n但是如果10个题全错，你可以拿到40分。\n也就是说，如果你十个题都有把握，你可以故意全选错来得到20分的bonus。但一旦有一个题出了偏差，你很有可能丢失20分左右。\n如果这是你擅长的科目，你敢故意十个题全选错吗", "timestamp": 1631806420, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1631878282, "url": "", "vote": {"vote_data": {"敢": 45, "不敢": 24, "内卷卷疯了": 42, "吃瓜": 15}, "vote_options": ["敢", "不敢", "内卷卷疯了", "吃瓜"]}}}